Fix CI error.

Thanks to @jrbenny35 for helping me figure this out!

Looks like CircleCI was trying to lint inside the ./firefox directory it creates when running our test commands. CI check was failing for a linting error in a script we didn't write:
"/home/circleci/checkout/firefox/defaults/pref/channel-prefs.js
5:1  error  'pref' is not defined  no-undef"
Add Under Construction note in README.md.
